# Drum Samples Directory

Place your GM MIDI drum samples here. Required files:
- kick.wav
- snare.wav
- snare_rim_open.wav
- snare_rim_closed.wav
- hihat_closed.wav
- hihat_open.wav
- crash.wav
- ride.wav
- ride_bell.wav
- splash.wav
- tom_low.wav
- tom_mid.wav
- tom_high.wav

Recommended sources:
- Salamander Drum Kit (CC0): https://github.com/sfztools/salamander-drumkit
- Freesound.org (search for CC0 drum samples)

If no samples are found, the app will fall back to synthesis mode.
